{"tid":601347,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Uber首宗自駕車撞死人片段曝光 警：Uber無錯","createTime":"2018-03-22T07:05:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T08:00:54.000Z","uid":161222,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3d6ae0ee69d5c2b8bc281721d41680de641945a5","tid":601347,"uid":161222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T07:05:47.000Z","msg":"Uber自動駕駛車在美國亞利桑那州撞死途人，警方周三公開行車紀錄儀的影片，當地傳媒引述警方初步調查指，相信Uber在今次事件中沒有犯錯。<br />\n<br />\n從行車記錄儀的影片看到，途人赫茨伯格（Elaine Herzberg）摸黑推單車過馬路，當時Uber的自動駕駛車照明系統在意外前幾秒才有光線照射到赫茨伯格身上，令人質疑「自動駕駛」汽車偵測到有障礙物時，是否能夠及時停車。<br />\n<br />\n此外，雖然當時該Uber車處於自動駕駛模式，但駕駛座有後備司機準備隨時掌軚。不過在拍攝司機的影片看到，司機當時眼睛向下望，一直沒有為意路面情況，直至撞到途人才一臉驚訝望向路面。<br />\n<br />\n警方周三公開影片，警方初步認為意外屬很難避免，警長摩亞(Sylvia Moir)指：「我懷疑初步看來，Uber在今次件事件中沒有錯。」但不排除起訴後備司機。<br />\n<br />\n今次是首宗涉及自動駕駛車的奪命意外，事後Uber宣佈暫停在美加的「自動駕駛」車試驗計劃。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180322/57979077\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180322%2F57979077&d=MsmEIM2wZNZ637CA7cgqp%2F6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=7b3d67b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180322%2F57979077&h=79f7353d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180322/57979077</a>"},{"pid":"0fb8ecddee2ab79ec39260bb2e9af270fe17b5a7","tid":601347,"uid":161222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T07:10:04.000Z","msg":"睇完條片，由見到架單車到撞埋去得兩三秒唔夠，換轉係人揸brake唔brake得切？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54f46b4349eaeb63a056c79fb6490a2c97b0c92c","tid":601347,"uid":83623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T07:10:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Cuo8eq9C3Ec\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCuo8eq9C3Ec&d=MsmEIM2wZNZ637CA7cgqp%2F6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010v